: null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016202, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "It is narrated from Asma binte Umais that she said: I saw her seated facing the Qibla during her illness, raising her hands to the heavens and saying…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Phir farmaya; kya jo mai dekh rahi hu aap bhi dekh rahe hai? Poochha kya dekh rahi hai, farmaya yeh ahle aasmaan ke daste hai, yeh Jibraeel (a) aur Paighambar (s) hai jo farma rahe hai; Ay meri beti aawo jo kuchh tere liye aage hai tere liye behtar hai.", "UrduDescription": "پھر فرمایا کیا جو میں دیکھ رہی ہوں آپ بھی دیکھ رہے ہیں؟ پوچھا کیا دیکھ رہی ہیں، فرمایا یہ اہل آسمان کے دستے ہیں، یہ جبرئیل اور یہ پیغمبر ہیں جو فرما رہے ہیں اے میری بیٹی آؤ جو کچھ تیرے لئے آگے ہے تیرے لئے بہتر ہے۔", "English": "Then she said: Can you all see what I see? She was asked: What can you see? She replied: These are the groups of the folks of heavens, and this is Jibraeel, and this is the Messenger of Allah, who is saying: Come, my child, whatever is before you is much better for you.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6"